	SHOW item

The SHOW command can be used to display various information depending on the 
value of 'item'.  The legal values are shown below, along with a decription 
of what each will display.

	Item		Information Displayed
        ----------------------------------------------------------------------
	SOUNDINGS	All soundings currently available, with their 
			id names, sites, and times

	FLAGS		The program flags and their current values

	COLORS		The color index names and the colors currently 
			associated with them

	ORIGIN		The current origin for (lat,lon) <--> (x,y) conversion

	LIMITS		The current contour limits for all fields
